memberdef.name: IncorrectRPCListLabel
memberdef.initializer:
= "Your project's RPC-list is full, so we can't add some RPCs just compiled.

By removing outdated RPCs, the list will be long enough but incompatible with older client builds!

Make sure you change the game version where you use PhotonNetwork.ConnectUsingSettings()."

memberdef.name: FullRPCListLabel
memberdef.initializer:
= "Your project's RPC-list is too long for PUN.

You can change PUN's source to use short-typed RPC index. Look for comments 'LIMITS RPC COUNT'

Alternatively, remove some RPC methods (use more parameters per RPC maybe).

After a RPC-list refresh, make sure you change the game version where you use PhotonNetwork.ConnectUsingSettings()."

memberdef.name: PUNNameReplaceLabel
memberdef.initializer: = "PUN replaces RPC names with numbers by using the RPC-list. All clients must use the same list for that.\n\nClearing it most likely makes your client incompatible with previous versions! Change your game version or make sure the RPC-list matches other clients."
